_sText:
FY_ARGENTINA!

This is a small funny map made by Pennywise. It got four towers and two spawns. You can walk either left or right but you can also take the risky way through the middle.

See below for installation instructions.

   1. Extract the zip archive.
   2. Put the 'maps' folder in your games/servers 'cstrike' folder. It's by default in:
             C:\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\*****\counter-strike source\cstrike.
   3. Start Counter-Strike: Source or your server.
   4. Enjoy!
